  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. Adding the like terms <span class=\"italic\">x</span> and <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"0 point 2 5 x \"></span> yields the equation <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, 1 point 2 5 x times, open parenthesis, 50 minus x, close parenthesis\"></span>. Substituting 20 for <span class=\"italic\">x</span> yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of 20 equals, open parenthesis, 1 point 2 5 times 20, close parenthesis, times, open parenthesis, 50 minus 20, close parenthesis\"></span>. The product <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"1 point 2 5 times 20 \"></span> is equal to 25, and the difference <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"50 minus 20 \"></span> is equal to 30. Substituting these values in the given equation gives <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of 20 equals, 25 times 30\"></span>, and multiplying 25 by 30 results in&nbsp;<span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of 20 equals 750\"></span>.<p>Choices A, B, and D are incorrect and may result from conceptual or computational errors when finding the value of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of 20\"></span>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>\n",
